::DarkMouse::

She tried and found she could move her arm a little.  She opened her 
eyes and saw the sky and trees around her.  She also saw a lazar 
blast fly over her head. She rolled over on her side and tried to 
move her legs.  She was wobbly but able to stand on all fours.  She 
looked around and saw two Preds under fire from someone in the bushes 
a ways off.  She looked for her pet but it was gone.  She felt sick 
about leaving her pet behind, but she knew she had to in order to 
survive.  She slowly walked off into the bushes and through the trees.
The tranc made her a little woozy, but it was slowly wearing off.
